      "message": "What you described was option 1.\n\nOption 2 is\n1. The url to the new build page will be: \n/ui/p/\u003cproject\u003e/buckets/\u003cbucket\u003e/builders/\u003cbuilder\u003e/builds/\u003cbuild_id\u003e.\n2. In the lagacy handler, check \"?forceLegacy\u003d1\" (or smth like this). if not present, redirect to the new page.\n\nWe will keep the /ui/ prefix.\n3. Later, when we ready to turn down old page, unconditionally redirects the old URL to /ui/p/\u003cproject\u003e/buckets/\u003cbucket\u003e/builders/\u003cbuilder\u003e/builds/\u003cbuild_id\u003e.\n\nPro:\nEasy to add new handlers at any point.\nCon:\nURL is longer.",
